{"id": "rios004", "name": "Audio_YazawaRI_495_03_20", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Unit 10! I found you!\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "Rin? I'm on patrol...\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Take a look at this flower! Its leaves are yellow, could it have been bitten by an insect?\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "Is this... the calendula that Dr. Yazawa bought you?\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Yeah, now I'm responsible for taking care of it, but I'm not a botanist...\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "Why not ask Dr. Yazawa and them to take a look?\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "No way! They'll yell at me for sure... \"How'd you let it get like this!\"...\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "Haha... Let me take a look.\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Scan_01", "Scans"], "content": ""}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "No sign of pest damage, but its color and hydration data reveal that its state of health is not optimal... Has it had enough sun?\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Not much, there's not a lot of sun in my room... What should I do?\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "The weather system in Node 03 is set for 12 hours of sunlight per day, beginning at 6 a.m.... All you need to do is let it get some sun for a period of time each day and its condition should improve.\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "But after class I always go to the research center...\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "Hmm... Why not ask the Architect at your home to help?\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "We haven't applied for home care, so there's no Architect there! Just us three.\nAh, Unit 10, do you want to come to our home?\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "M-Me...?\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Yeah, that way we can talk every day. I have nothing to do when I don't go to the research center.\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "B-But, I've been sent here for work... If the Yazawa family applies, according to the rules, another Architect will be sent to your home...\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Oh... So it's not possible?\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "... That is correct.\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Darnit, Architects' are so frustrating.\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "Haha... We were designed to be like this.\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "You're the only one who's different... I feel like there's something special about you. Hmm, well are there any other units like you? One that laughs, gets scared, can think...\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "I-I'm not that special. Rin... I must still obey commands.\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "But don't you think work is a drag? You're helping people do stuff all day and never get a chance to rest.\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "I...\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Be honest, Unit 10.\nI always feel like doing homework sucks──\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "Yes... But you must continue to attend to your studies at the Academy.\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">... Yes! At the Academy!</font>\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "Wah! That was sudden...\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "I can let the flower get some sun in my Academy! The Architects and drones won't care, and mom and dad won't see it... Plus, that way I won't have to take care of it every day!\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "So that's been the point all along...\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Hehe, you got it. Unit 10, help me keep this a secret! You can't tell mom and dad!\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["sound_imnotification", "Notification"], "content": ""}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Wah! What's that light?\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "It means I still have work to do... Sorry, Rin. I must return. I hope I will have time to see you in a bit...\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "Rin?\n\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "I've always wanted to ask... Unit 10, don't you think our voices sound very similar?\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "Eh? Voices?\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "I noticed it a long time ago! If you don't believe me then take a listen.\nAh~Ahhh~\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "...! You're right... Quite similar.\nHowever, Architect's voices are formed randomly. There's no set rule... Perhaps it's just a coincidence.\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "... Perhaps...\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "10号機！いた！\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "凛？\n私今は巡回中で……\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "そんなことより！これ見て！\n葉っぱが黄色くなっちゃったの……\nもしかして虫かな？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "そのキンセンカは……前矢澤博士が買ってくれた……\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "うん。そうなの。\nでも、私植物学者じゃないから……\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "矢澤博士たちに見せてみたら？\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "そんなことできるわけないよ！\n絶対怒られるもん……\n「なんでちゃんと面倒見ないの！」って……\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "あはは……見せて。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Scan_01", "スキャン"], "content": ""}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "害虫はついてないみたい。\nでも、葉っぱの光沢感と含水量の数値がこの子の健康状態が良くないことを示してる……\n日光には当ててあげてる？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "あんまりかも。\n私の部屋、日の光があんまり当たらないから……\nどうしよう？\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "Node03の天気システムは1日12時間、朝6時から太陽が出る設定になってる……\n毎日少しでも日光の当たるところに出してあげれば、ちょっとずつ良くなるはずだよ。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "でも、私放課後はずっと研究所にいるし……\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "なら……家のアーキテクトに頼むとか？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "うち家事代行サービスは頼んでないから……\nだから家族3人だけで、アーキテクトはいないんだ！\nあっ！10号機、うちに来たくない？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "わっ……私？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "うん！\nそうすれば、毎日お話できるし。\n研究所に来ない日は、何をしたらいいのかわからないんだよね……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "で、でも……私はこの研究所に派遣されたアーキテクトだから……\n矢澤家が申請を出しても、派遣されるのは他のアーキテクトだと思う……\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "ええ～……絶対に無理なのかな？\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……無理だよ。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "やだなぁ～\nアーキテクトって頭硬いんだもん。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "あはは……そういう風にインプットされてるからね。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "10号機だけが違うの……\nやっぱりあなたって特別。\nねぇ、他にもあなたみたいなアーキテクトっているの？\n笑ったり、怖がったり、考えたりするアーキテクト……\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "わ、私は特別なんかじゃ……\n……指令はやっぱり絶対だから。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "でも、あなたでも仕事が嫌になる時はあるでしょ？\n毎日毎日みんなのために働いてさ。\n休憩もできないし。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "それは……\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "ここだけの話だから！\nね？10号機。本当のところどうなの？\n私はよく宿題やだなぁって思うよ──\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "うん……アカデミーにはちゃんと行かないとだめだよ。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">……あああ！アカデミー！</font>\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "きゃっ！突然なに……\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "アカデミーに持って行って日に当ててあげればいいんだ！\nアーキテクトもドローンも何も言わないし、お父さんお母さんにもバレない……\nそれに……毎日面倒見なくて済むし！\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "後半が凛の本心だよね……\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "えへへ、バレちゃった。\n10号機、これは私たちだけの秘密だよ！\nお父さんお母さんには内緒だからね！\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["sound_imnotification", "通知"], "content": ""}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "わっ！光った……\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "仕事の合図だ……\nごめんね、凛。私行かないと。\nまた後で会えるといいんだけど……\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "凛？\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "ずーっと聞きたかったんだけどさ……私たちの声って似てるって思わない？\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "え？声？\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "ずっとそう思ってたの！\n信じられないなら聞いてみてよ。\nあ～あ～\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……！本当……そっくり……\nでも、アーキテクトの声はランダム合成だから、決まりはないの……\nただの偶然……だね。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……かもね……\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "十號機！找到妳了！\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "凜？我正在巡邏……\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "先幫我看看這朵花嘛！葉子都黃了，該不會是被蟲咬了吧？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "這盆金盞花……是之前矢澤博士買給妳的？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "嗯，現在變成我在照顧它，但我又不是植物學博士……\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "請矢澤博士他們看一看呢？\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "不行啦！肯定會被他們罵的……「妳怎麼把它養成這樣！」……\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "哈哈……我檢查一下。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Scan_01", "掃描"], "content": ""}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "沒有蟲害狀況，但色澤與含水量數據顯示，它的健康狀況不佳……有讓它曬太陽嗎？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "比較少耶，我房間曬不到太陽……該怎麼辦？\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "Node 03 的天氣系統設定一日 12 小時日照，從早上六點開始……只要每天讓它曬一陣子，應該會慢慢好轉。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "可是我下課後都會過來研究所……\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "那……請家裡的建造者幫忙？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "我家沒有申請照護服務，所以沒有其他建造者喔！只有我們三個人。\n啊，十號機想不想來我們家？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "我……我嗎？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "對啊，這樣我們就能天天聊天了。沒來研究所的日子都不知道做什麼才好……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "可、可是，我是被分派到這裡工作的……如果矢澤家提出申請，按規定也會由其他建造者去……\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "唔……沒辦法嗎？\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……沒辦法呢。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "討厭，建造者都是一群死腦筋。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "哈哈……我們就是這樣子被設計出來的。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "只有妳不一樣呢……越來越覺得十號機很特別了。吶，有其他機體和妳一樣嗎？會笑、會害怕、會思考……\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "我、我沒有那麼特別啦，凜……指令還是必須遵守的。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "但妳也會覺得工作很煩吧？畢竟妳們每天都在幫大家做事，都沒怎麼休息。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "這個……\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "誠實一點嘛，十號機。\n我也常常覺得要寫作業好麻煩呢──\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "嗯……學院還是要好好去喔。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">……對了！學院！</font>\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "哇！怎麼突然……\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "我可以把花搬去學院曬太陽！建造者跟無人機都不會管，爸媽也不會看到……而且，這樣我就不用天天照顧它了！\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "後面那句才是凜真正的想法嗎……\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "嘻嘻，被妳發現了。十號機，幫我保守秘密！不可以跟我爸媽說喔！\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["sound_imnotification", "通知"], "content": ""}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "哇！燈亮了？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "這是有工作要做的意思……抱歉，凜，我得回去了。希望等等還有空見面……\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "凜？\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "我一直想問……十號機，妳不覺得我們的聲音很像嗎？\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "欸？聲音？\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "我好久以前就注意到了！不信妳聽聽看。\n啊～啊～\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……！真的……好像喔。\n可是，建造者的聲音都是隨機合成，沒有一定的規律……也許只是巧合。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……也許吧……\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "10호기! 여깄었구나!\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "Rin? 나는 지금 순찰 중이라...\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "먼저 이 꽃 좀 봐주지 않을래? 잎사귀가 전부 노랗게 됐는데, 벌레가 먹어서 이렇게 된 건 아니겠지?\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "이 카렌듈라(Calendula)는...예전에 Yazawa 박사님이 사주신 거 아니야?\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "맞아. 지금은 내가 돌보고 있는데, 내가 식물학 박사도 아니고...\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "Yazawa 박사님들께 보여드리는 게 어때?\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "안 돼! 분명 혼낼 거야... \"너, 대체 어떻게 했길래 이걸 이 지경으로 만든 거니!\"라고 말이야...\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "하하... 내가 한번 봐볼게.\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Scan_01", "스캐닝"], "content": ""}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "벌레에 의한 손상은 없어. 하지만 색소와 수분 수치로 봤을 때, 현재 건강 상태가 좋은 것은 아닌 것 같아... 햇빛은 쬐게 해줬어?\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "자주는 아니지만... 내 방에는 햇빛이 별로 안 들어오거든... 어떡하지?\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "Node 03의 날씨 시스템이 설정한 일조 시간은 하루 12시간으로, 오전 6시부터야... 매일 조금씩 햇빛을 쬐게 해주면 분명 조금씩 나아질 거야.\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "하지만 난 수업 끝나면 항상 연구소로 오는데...\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "그렇다면... 집에 있는 아키텍트에게 부탁하는 것은?\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "우리집은 집안 돌봄 서비스를 신청 안 했기 때문에 집에 아키텍트가 없는 상황이라구! 집에는 아빠, 엄마, 나 이렇게 세 사람밖에 없어.\n 아, 10호기가 우리집에 오는 건 어떨까?\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "내... 내가?\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "응! 그럼 우리도 매일 같이 얘기도 나눌 수 있고 좋잖아! 연구소에 오지 않는 날은 나도 집에서 혼자 뭘 해야 할지 잘 모르겠거든...\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "하, 하지만 나는 이곳의 업무를 위해 파견된 아키텍트라서... 만약에 규정대로라면 Yazawa 씨가 돌봄 서비스 신청을 하게 될 때, 다른 아키텍트가 파견될 거야...\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "아... 그럼 방법이 없는 거야?\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "....응.\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "하여간 정말! 아키텍트는 모두 생각이란 걸 할 줄 모르나!\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "하하... 우리들은 애초부터 모두 그렇게 설계되었으니까.\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "너만 빼고 말이지... 10호기는 점점 더 뭔가 특별해지고 있는 것 같아. 아, 혹시 너랑 같은 증상인 기체도 있어? 웃을 수도 있고 뭔가를 두려워하기도 하고 생각에 잠기기도 한다는 등...\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "나, 나는 딱히 특별하지 않아...\nRin.... 그래도 지령은 제대로 준수하고 있어.\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "하지만 너도 일하는 건 싫어하지 않아? 매일 다른 사람을 도와 일해야만 하잖아. 쉬지도 못하고.\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "그건...\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "10호기, 좀 솔직해지시지?\n나도 매일 숙제하는 거 똑같이 싫어하거든.\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "음.... 그래도 아카데미는 잘 다니도록 해.\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">...그렇구나! 아카데미가 있었어!</font>\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "으앗! 갑자기 왜 큰소리로 아카데미를...\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "꽃을 아카데미에 가지고 가서 태양을 쬐게 해주는 거야! 아키텍트랑 드론도 모두 신경도 안 쓸테고 아빠랑 엄마한테도 안 들킬 수 있을 테니까... 게다가... 그렇게 하면 굳이 내가 매일 돌봐주지 않아도 되잖아!\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "마지막에 말한 것이 Rin의 진짜 목적 아닌가...\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "헤헤, 들켜버렸네. 10호기, 꼭 비밀 지켜줘야 해! 엄마랑 아빠한테 절대 말하면 안 돼!\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["sound_imnotification", "통지"], "content": ""}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "앗? 불이 들어왔어?\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "이건 이제 업무를 수행해야 한다는 뜻이야.... 미안, Rin, 나는 이제 가봐야 해. 나중에 시간이 날 때 다시 만나서 얘기하자...\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "Rin?\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "계속 물어보고 싶었는데... 10호기, 네가 봤을 때 우리들 목소리, 뭔가 닮지 않았어?\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "응? 목소리가?\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "옛날부터 그렇게 느꼈었다고! 잘 들어봐.\n 아~ 아아~\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "...! 정말... 비슷하네.\n 하지만 아키텍트의 목소리는 모두 랜덤으로 합성되는데... 목소리에 대한 규격은 따로 없거든... 그러니 아마도 우연이겠지.\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "...그렇겠지...?\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "十號機！找到妳了！\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "凜？我正在巡邏……\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "先幫我看看這朵花嘛！葉子都黃了，該不會是被蟲咬了吧？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "這盆金盞花……是之前矢澤博士買給妳的？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "嗯，現在變成我在照顧它，但我又不是植物學博士……\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "請矢澤博士他們看一看呢？\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "不行啦！肯定會被他們罵的……「妳怎麼把它養成這樣！」……\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "哈哈……我檢查一下。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Scan_01", "掃描"], "content": ""}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "沒有蟲害狀況，但色澤與含水量數據顯示，它的健康狀況不佳……有讓它曬太陽嗎？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "比較少耶，我房間曬不到太陽……該怎麼辦？\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "Node 03 的天氣系統設定一日 12 小時日照，從早上六點開始……只要每天讓它曬一陣子，應該會慢慢好轉。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "可是我下課後都會過來研究所……\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "那……請家裡的建造者幫忙？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "我家沒有申請照護服務，所以沒有其他建造者喔！只有我們三個人。\n啊，十號機想不想來我們家？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "我……我嗎？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "對啊，這樣我們就能天天聊天了。沒來研究所的日子都不知道做什麼才好……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "可、可是，我是被分派到這裡工作的……如果矢澤家提出申請，按規定也會由其他建造者去……\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "唔……沒辦法嗎？\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……沒辦法呢。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "討厭，建造者都是一群死腦筋。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "哈哈……我們就是這樣子被設計出來的。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "只有妳不一樣呢……越來越覺得十號機很特別了。吶，有其他機體和妳一樣嗎？會笑、會害怕、會思考……\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "我、我沒有那麼特別啦，凜……指令還是必須遵守的。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "但妳也會覺得工作很煩吧？畢竟妳們每天都在幫大家做事，都沒怎麼休息。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "這個……\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "誠實一點嘛，十號機。\n我也常常覺得要寫作業好麻煩呢──\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "嗯……學院還是要好好去喔。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">……對了！學院！</font>\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "哇！怎麼突然……\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "我可以把花搬去學院曬太陽！建造者跟無人機都不會管，爸媽也不會看到……而且，這樣我就不用天天照顧它了！\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "後面那句才是凜真正的想法嗎……\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "嘻嘻，被妳發現了。十號機，幫我保守秘密！不可以跟我爸媽說喔！\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["sound_imnotification", "通知"], "content": ""}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "哇！燈亮了？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "這是有工作要做的意思……抱歉，凜，我得回去了。希望等等還有空見面……\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "凜？\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "我一直想問……十號機，妳不覺得我們的聲音很像嗎？\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "欸？聲音？\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "我好久以前就注意到了！不信妳聽聽看。\n啊～啊～\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……！真的……好像喔。\n可是，建造者的聲音都是隨機合成，沒有一定的規律……也許只是巧合。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……也許吧……\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "十号机！找到妳了！\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "凛？我正在巡逻……\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "先帮我看看这朵花嘛！叶子都黄了，该不会是被虫咬了吧？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "这盆金盏花……是之前矢泽博士买给妳的？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "嗯，现在变成我在照顾它，但我又不是植物学博士……\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "请矢泽博士他们看一看呢？\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "不行啦！肯定会被他们骂的……「妳怎么把它养成这样！」……\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "哈哈……我检查一下。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Scan_01", "扫描"], "content": ""}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "没有虫害状况，但色泽与含水量数据显示，它的健康状况不佳……有让它晒太阳吗？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "比较少耶，我房间晒不到太阳……该怎么办？\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "Node 03 的天气系统设定一日 12 小时日照，从早上六点开始……只要每天让它晒一阵子，应该会慢慢好转。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "可是我下课后都会过来研究所……\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "那……请家里的建造者帮忙？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "我家没有申请照护服务，所以没有其他建造者喔！只有我们三个人。\n啊，十号机想不想来我们家？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "我……我吗？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "对啊，这样我们就能天天聊天了。没来研究所的日子都不知道做什么才好……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "可、可是，我是被分派到这里工作的……如果矢泽家提出申请，按规定也会由其他建造者去……\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "唔……没办法吗？\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……没办法呢。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "讨厌，建造者都是一群死脑筋。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "哈哈……我们就是这样子被设计出来的。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "只有妳不一样呢……越来越觉得十号机很特别了。呐，有其他机体和妳一样吗？会笑、会害怕、会思考……\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "我、我没有那么特别啦，凛……指令还是必须遵守的。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "但妳也会觉得工作很烦吧？毕竟妳们每天都在帮大家做事，都没怎么休息。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "这个……\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "诚实一点嘛，十号机。\n我也常常觉得要写作业好麻烦呢──\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "嗯……学院还是要好好去喔。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">……对了！学院！ </font>\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "哇！怎么突然……\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "我可以把花搬去学院晒太阳！建造者跟无人机都不会管，爸妈也不会看到……而且，这样我就不用天天照顾它了！\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "后面那句才是凛真正的想法吗……\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "嘻嘻，被妳发现了。十号机，帮我保守秘密！不可以跟我爸妈说喔！\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["sound_imnotification", "通知"], "content": ""}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "哇！灯亮了？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "这是有工作要做的意思……抱歉，凛，我得回去了。希望等等还有空见面……\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "凛？\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "我一直想问……十号机，妳不觉得我们的声音很像吗？\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "欸？声音？\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "我好久以前就注意到了！不信妳听听看。\n啊～啊～\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……！真的……好像喔。\n可是，建造者的声音都是随机合成，没有一定的规律……也许只是巧合。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……也许吧……\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[讯号中断]</i>\n"}]]}